quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  23,51,"Mwebwe ntumwa z’Imana, nimufungure ibifungurwa vyiza kandi mugire ibikorwa vyiza, mu vy’ukuri jewe ndafise ubumenyi bw’ivyo mugira vyose"
  23,52,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\taba\tbantu\tbanyu\tn’abantu\tbamwe,\tnanje\tnd’Umuremyi wanyu, rero nimuntinye"
  23,53,"Mugabo bararicagaguye ijambo ryabo ryari hagati yabo barishira kure na kure, hanyuma umurwi umwe umwe waranezerejwe nivyo bafise"
  23,54,Ni mubareke nuko kutibuka kwabo kugeza kugihe cagenywe
  23,55,Mbega bariyumvira muvyo twabahaye mumatungo hamwe n’ibibondo
  23,56,"Egome, tubatanguriza kubaha mubintu vyiza mugabo ntavyo bazi"
  23,57,Mu vy’ukuri abo batinya Umuremyi wabo n’abagamburutsi
  23,58,Nabo amajambo y’Umuremyi wabo bayemera
  23,59,Nabo Umuremyi wabo batamu gereranya n’ibindi bintu
  23,60,"Nabo\tbatanga\tmuvyo\tbahawe\tn’Imana,\tmugihe\timitima\tyabo\titinya kubera yuko bazosubizwa ku Muremyi wabo"
  23,61,Abo bose nibo bagira umwete w’ibikorwa mubintu vy’ineza kandi nibo baja imbere muri ivyo bikorwa
  23,62,"Natwe ntiduhatagiza umutima w’umuntu atari nkuko wifashe wonyene kandi turafise igitabu kivugisha ukuri, rero ntibazo hemukirwa"
  23,63,Mugabo imitima yabo isamajijwe nivyo nyene kandi barafise ibikorwa bagira bitari ivyo
  23,64,"Kugeza aho tuzoba hamagarira mubihano bamwe muba nezereza babo, aho niho bazokoma induru"
  23,65,"Ntimukome induru kuri uno musi, ntankeka mwebwe ntimuzofashwa na twebwe"
  23,66,Mu vy’ukuri amajambo yanje yarasomwa kuri mwebwe mugabo mwaca musubira inyuma n’ibitsintsiri vyanyu
  23,67,Mwishima muganira mw’ijoro kuri iyi Qur’aani muyikengera
  23,68,Mbega ntibiyumviriye ijambo canke bashikiriwe n’ibitashikiye abavyeyi babo baho hambere
  23,69,Canke ntibamenye intumwa yabo kukaba arico gituma bamuhakana
  23,70,Canke bavuga yuko ari umusazi ahubwo yabashikiye munzira y’ukuri kandi benshi muribo nabanka ukuri aho kuri
  23,71,"Iyo hakurikizwa ukuri ivyo bipfuza vy’Amajuru n’Isi vyari kwononekara hamwe n’ibiri murivyo vyose, mugabo twarabazaniye icibutso cabo nabo bagishira kure nico cibutso cabo"
  23,72,"Canke urabasaba impembo, mugabo impembo y’Umuremyi wawe niyo nziza gusumba, nayo niyo nziza mubatanzi b’imigisha yayo"
  23,73,Mu vy’ukuri wewe ubahamagarira munzira igororotse
  23,74,Na bamwe batemera umusi w’umuhero w’Isi bari kure niyi nzira igororotse
  23,75,Naho twari kubasabira impuhwe nukubakurira ingorane zabo bafise ntankeka bari kubandanya muri iyo nzira y’ubuzimire bwabo naho borengana bari muri ayo mabi yabo barimwo
  23,76,Mu vy’ukuri twarabahanye mugabo ntibigeze batumbera ku Muremyi wabo canke ngo bayigamburukire
  23,77,"Kugeza aho twabugurira umuryango w’ibihano bikaze cane, aho niho baciye bihebura"